      • clean

        public void clean()
           throws IOException
        This method uses HivePartitionVersionFinder to list out versions corresponding to this dataset. It will then filter out versions using HivePartitionVersionPolicy. For each version there will be a corresponding VersionCleaner which will clean the version.
